{"componentChunkName":"component---src-templates-post-template-tsx","path":"/tech/2024-08-01-DebounceВЎђ-Throttle/","result":{"data":{"allMarkdownRemark":{"edges":[{"node":{"html":"<h2 id=\"1-debounce\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#1-debounce\" aria-label=\"1 debounce permalink\" class=\"anchor-header before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" height=\"20\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"20\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>1. Debounce</h2>\n<p><code class=\"language-text\">Debounce</code>віћ ВЌ░ВєЇВаЂВю╝вАю в░юВЃЮьЋўвіћ ВЮ┤в▓цьіИвЦ╝ ЖиИвБ╣ьЎћьЋўВЌг ВЮ┤в▓цьіИЖ░ђ 1в▓ѕвДї ВІцьќЅьЋўвЈёвАЮ ьЋўвіћ ЖИ░ВѕаВЮ┤вІц.<br>\nВЮ┤в▓цьіИЖ░ђ в░юВЃЮьЋўвЕ┤ ьЃђВЮ┤веИвЦ╝ ВёцВаЋьЋўЖ│а, ьЃђВЮ┤веИЖ░ђ вЂЮвѓўЖИ░ ВаёВЌљ ВЮ┤в▓цьіИЖ░ђ в░юВЃЮьЋўвЕ┤ ьЃђВЮ┤веИЖ░ђ 0В┤ѕвХђьё░ вІцВІю ВІюВъЉьЋювІц.</p>\n<h2 id=\"11-trailing-debounce\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#11-trailing-debounce\" aria-label=\"11 trailing debounce permalink\" class=\"anchor-header before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" height=\"20\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"20\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>1.1 Trailing Debounce</h2>\n<p><code class=\"language-text\">Trailing Debounce</code>віћ ВЌ░ВєЇВаЂВЮИ ВЮ┤в▓цьіИвЊц ВцЉ вДѕВДђвДЅ ВЮ┤в▓цьіИвДї ВІцьќЅьЋўвЈёвАЮ ьЋўвіћ в░ЕВІЮВЮ┤вІц.\r\n<span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; max-width: 768px; \"\n    >\n      <a\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-link\"\n    href=\"/static/32495b48e0fe681aee80393c10cf0c18/bbbf7/image-1.png\"\n    style=\"display: block\"\n    target=\"_blank\"\n    rel=\"noopener\"\n  >\n    <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 26.041666666666668%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/png;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n  ></span>\n  <picture>\n          <source\n              srcset=\"/static/32495b48e0fe681aee80393c10cf0c18/a59e9/image-1.webp 192w,\n/static/32495b48e0fe681aee80393c10cf0c18/0ca9f/image-1.webp 384w,\n/static/32495b48e0fe681aee80393c10cf0c18/dc9b9/image-1.webp 768w,\n/static/32495b48e0fe681aee80393c10cf0c18/e2c2f/image-1.webp 1152w,\n/static/32495b48e0fe681aee80393c10cf0c18/94b1e/image-1.webp 1280w\"\n              sizes=\"(max-width: 768px) 100vw, 768px\"\n              type=\"image/webp\"\n            />\n          <source\n            srcset=\"/static/32495b48e0fe681aee80393c10cf0c18/3b721/image-1.png 192w,\n/static/32495b48e0fe681aee80393c10cf0c18/66595/image-1.png 384w,\n/static/32495b48e0fe681aee80393c10cf0c18/fe486/image-1.png 768w,\n/static/32495b48e0fe681aee80393c10cf0c18/d2d74/image-1.png 1152w,\n/static/32495b48e0fe681aee80393c10cf0c18/bbbf7/image-1.png 1280w\"\n            sizes=\"(max-width: 768px) 100vw, 768px\"\n            type=\"image/png\"\n          />\n          <img\n            class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n            src=\"/static/32495b48e0fe681aee80393c10cf0c18/fe486/image-1.png\"\n            alt=\"alt text\"\n            title=\"\"\n            loading=\"lazy\"\n            decoding=\"async\"\n            style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;\"\n          />\n        </picture>\n  </a>\n    </span>\r\nЖиИвд╝Ж│╝ Ж░ЎВЮ┤ ВЌ░ВєЇВаЂВЮИ ВЮ┤в▓цьіИвЊц ВцЉ вДѕВДђвДЅ ВЮ┤в▓цьіИвЦ╝ ВёаьЃЮьЋўвЕ░ ьЃђВЮ┤веИЖ░ђ вЂЮвѓгВЮё вЋї ВЮ┤в▓цьіИЖ░ђ ВІцьќЅвљювІц.</p>\n<h2 id=\"12-leading-debounce\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#12-leading-debounce\" aria-label=\"12 leading debounce permalink\" class=\"anchor-header before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" height=\"20\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"20\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>1.2 Leading Debounce</h2>\n<p><code class=\"language-text\">Leading Debounce</code>віћ ВЌ░ВєЇВаЂВЮИ ВЮ┤в▓цьіИвЊц ВцЉ В▓Фв▓ѕВДИ ВЮ┤в▓цьіИвДї ВІцьќЅьЋўвЈёвАЮ ьЋўвіћ в░ЕВІЮВЮ┤вІц.\r\n<span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; max-width: 768px; \"\n    >\n      <a\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-link\"\n    href=\"/static/f20b66456e86b0b212ef679b92e89f3b/bbbf7/image-2.png\"\n    style=\"display: block\"\n    target=\"_blank\"\n    rel=\"noopener\"\n  >\n    <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 26.5625%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/png;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n  ></span>\n  <picture>\n          <source\n              srcset=\"/static/f20b66456e86b0b212ef679b92e89f3b/a59e9/image-2.webp 192w,\n/static/f20b66456e86b0b212ef679b92e89f3b/0ca9f/image-2.webp 384w,\n/static/f20b66456e86b0b212ef679b92e89f3b/dc9b9/image-2.webp 768w,\n/static/f20b66456e86b0b212ef679b92e89f3b/e2c2f/image-2.webp 1152w,\n/static/f20b66456e86b0b212ef679b92e89f3b/94b1e/image-2.webp 1280w\"\n              sizes=\"(max-width: 768px) 100vw, 768px\"\n              type=\"image/webp\"\n            />\n          <source\n            srcset=\"/static/f20b66456e86b0b212ef679b92e89f3b/3b721/image-2.png 192w,\n/static/f20b66456e86b0b212ef679b92e89f3b/66595/image-2.png 384w,\n/static/f20b66456e86b0b212ef679b92e89f3b/fe486/image-2.png 768w,\n/static/f20b66456e86b0b212ef679b92e89f3b/d2d74/image-2.png 1152w,\n/static/f20b66456e86b0b212ef679b92e89f3b/bbbf7/image-2.png 1280w\"\n            sizes=\"(max-width: 768px) 100vw, 768px\"\n            type=\"image/png\"\n          />\n          <img\n            class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n            src=\"/static/f20b66456e86b0b212ef679b92e89f3b/fe486/image-2.png\"\n            alt=\"alt text\"\n            title=\"\"\n            loading=\"lazy\"\n            decoding=\"async\"\n            style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;\"\n          />\n        </picture>\n  </a>\n    </span>\r\nЖиИвд╝Ж│╝ Ж░ЎВЮ┤ В▓ўВЮї ВЮ┤в▓цьіИЖ░ђ в░юВЃЮьЋўвЕ┤ ВдЅВІю ВІцьќЅвљўвЕ░ ВЮ┤ьЏё ьЃђВЮ┤веИвЦ╝ ВЮ┤ВџЕьЋўВЌг ВЮ┤в▓цьіИЖ░ђ ВІцьќЅвљўВДђ ВЋівЈёвАЮ ьЋювІц.</p>\n<h2 id=\"13-debounce-hook-Жхгьўё\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#13-debounce-hook-%EA%B5%AC%ED%98%84\" aria-label=\"13 debounce hook Жхгьўё permalink\" class=\"anchor-header before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" height=\"20\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"20\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>1.3 Debounce Hook Жхгьўё</h2>\n<p>вІцВЮїВЮђ ВъЁваЦ ВЮ┤в▓цьіИвЦ╝ в░ЏВЋё Trailing DebounceвЦ╝ ЖхгьўёьЋю HookВЮ┤вІц.</p>\n<div\n              class=\"gatsby-code-button-container\"\n              data-toaster-id=\"82918728266826140000\"\n              data-toaster-class=\"gatsby-code-button-toaster\"\n              data-toaster-text-class=\"gatsby-code-button-toaster-text\"\n              data-toaster-text=\"­ЪЊІ  ВйћвЊювЦ╝ в│хВѓгьќѕВіхвІѕвІц.\"\n              data-toaster-duration=\"3000\"\n              onClick=\"copyToClipboard(`interface debounceProps<T> {\r\n  value: T;\r\n  delay: number;\r\n}\r\n\r\nfunction useDebounce<T>({ value, delay }: debounceProps<T>): T {\r\n  const [debouncedValue, setDebouncedValue] = useState(value);\r\n\r\n  useEffect(() => {\r\n    // ьЃђВЮ┤веИ ВЮ┤ьЏё вДѕВДђвДЅ valueвЦ╝ ВёаьЃЮ(Trailing Debounce)\r\n    const handler = setTimeout(() => {\r\n      setDebouncedValue(value);\r\n    }, delay);\r\n\r\n    // valueЖ░ђ в│ђЖ▓й вљўвЕ┤ ьЃђВЮ┤веИвЦ╝ В┤ѕЖИ░ьЎћ\r\n    return () => {\r\n      clearTimeout(handler);\r\n    };\r\n  }, [value]);\r\n\r\n  return debouncedValue;\r\n}`, `82918728266826140000`)\"\n            >\n              <div\n                class=\"gatsby-code-button\"\n                data-tooltip=\"\"\n              >\n                copy<svg stroke=\"currentColor\" fill=\"none\" stroke-width=\"2\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" class=\"h-4 w-4\" height=\"1em\" width=\"1em\" xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\"><path d=\"M16 4h2a2 2 0 0 1 2 2v14a2 2 0 0 1-2 2H6a2 2 0 0 1-2-2V6a2 2 0 0 1 2-2h2\"></path><rect x=\"8\" y=\"2\" width=\"8\" height=\"4\" rx=\"1\" ry=\"1\"></rect></svg>\n              </div>\n            </div>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"ts\"><pre class=\"language-ts\"><code class=\"language-ts\"><span class=\"token keyword\">interface</span> <span class=\"token class-name\">debounceProps<span class=\"token operator\">&lt;</span><span class=\"token constant\">T</span><span class=\"token operator\">></span></span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\r\n  value<span class=\"token operator\">:</span> <span class=\"token constant\">T</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\r\n  delay<span class=\"token operator\">:</span> <span class=\"token builtin\">number</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\r\n<span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span>\r\n\r\n<span class=\"token keyword\">function</span> <span class=\"token generic-function\"><span class=\"token function\">useDebounce</span><span class=\"token generic class-name\"><span class=\"token operator\">&lt;</span><span class=\"token constant\">T</span><span class=\"token operator\">></span></span></span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span> value<span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> delay <span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span><span class=\"token operator\">:</span> debounceProps<span class=\"token operator\">&lt;</span><span class=\"token constant\">T</span><span class=\"token operator\">></span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token operator\">:</span> <span class=\"token constant\">T</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\r\n  <span class=\"token keyword\">const</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">[</span>debouncedValue<span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> setDebouncedValue<span class=\"token punctuation\">]</span> <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> <span class=\"token function\">useState</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span>value<span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\r\n\r\n  <span class=\"token function\">useEffect</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span> <span class=\"token operator\">=></span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\r\n    <span class=\"token comment\">// ьЃђВЮ┤веИ ВЮ┤ьЏё вДѕВДђвДЅ valueвЦ╝ ВёаьЃЮ(Trailing Debounce)</span>\r\n    <span class=\"token keyword\">const</span> handler <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> <span class=\"token function\">setTimeout</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span> <span class=\"token operator\">=></span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\r\n      <span class=\"token function\">setDebouncedValue</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span>value<span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\r\n    <span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> delay<span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\r\n\r\n    <span class=\"token comment\">// valueЖ░ђ в│ђЖ▓й вљўвЕ┤ ьЃђВЮ┤веИвЦ╝ В┤ѕЖИ░ьЎћ</span>\r\n    <span class=\"token keyword\">return</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span> <span class=\"token operator\">=></span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\r\n      <span class=\"token function\">clearTimeout</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span>handler<span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\r\n    <span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\r\n  <span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">[</span>value<span class=\"token punctuation\">]</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\r\n\r\n  <span class=\"token keyword\">return</span> debouncedValue<span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\r\n<span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span></code></pre></div>\n<h2 id=\"2-throttle\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#2-throttle\" aria-label=\"2 throttle permalink\" class=\"anchor-header before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" height=\"20\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"20\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>2. Throttle</h2>\n<p><code class=\"language-text\">Throttle</code>ВЮђ ьЋюв▓ѕ ВІцьќЅвљўвЕ┤ ВЮ╝ВаЋ ВІюЖ░ё вЈЎВЋѕ вІцВІю ВІцьќЅвљўВДђ ВЋівЈёвАЮ ьЋўвіћ ЖИ░ВѕаВЮ┤вІц.<br>\nВдЅ, ВЮ╝ВаЋ ВІюЖ░ё Ж░ёЖ▓ЕВЌљВёю Вхювїђ 1в▓ѕвДї ВЮ┤в▓цьіИЖ░ђ ВІцьќЅвљўвЈёвАЮ ьЋювІц.</p>\n<p><span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; max-width: 768px; \"\n    >\n      <a\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-link\"\n    href=\"/static/6cbd58dc202b2c66c89b2033d6c25aa3/78ab2/image-3.png\"\n    style=\"display: block\"\n    target=\"_blank\"\n    rel=\"noopener\"\n  >\n    <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 53.645833333333336%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/png;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n  ></span>\n  <picture>\n          <source\n              srcset=\"/static/6cbd58dc202b2c66c89b2033d6c25aa3/a59e9/image-3.webp 192w,\n/static/6cbd58dc202b2c66c89b2033d6c25aa3/0ca9f/image-3.webp 384w,\n/static/6cbd58dc202b2c66c89b2033d6c25aa3/dc9b9/image-3.webp 768w,\n/static/6cbd58dc202b2c66c89b2033d6c25aa3/e2c2f/image-3.webp 1152w,\n/static/6cbd58dc202b2c66c89b2033d6c25aa3/c6649/image-3.webp 1201w\"\n              sizes=\"(max-width: 768px) 100vw, 768px\"\n              type=\"image/webp\"\n            />\n          <source\n            srcset=\"/static/6cbd58dc202b2c66c89b2033d6c25aa3/3b721/image-3.png 192w,\n/static/6cbd58dc202b2c66c89b2033d6c25aa3/66595/image-3.png 384w,\n/static/6cbd58dc202b2c66c89b2033d6c25aa3/fe486/image-3.png 768w,\n/static/6cbd58dc202b2c66c89b2033d6c25aa3/d2d74/image-3.png 1152w,\n/static/6cbd58dc202b2c66c89b2033d6c25aa3/78ab2/image-3.png 1201w\"\n            sizes=\"(max-width: 768px) 100vw, 768px\"\n            type=\"image/png\"\n          />\n          <img\n            class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n            src=\"/static/6cbd58dc202b2c66c89b2033d6c25aa3/fe486/image-3.png\"\n            alt=\"alt text\"\n            title=\"\"\n            loading=\"lazy\"\n            decoding=\"async\"\n            style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;\"\n          />\n        </picture>\n  </a>\n    </span></p>\n<p>Вюё ЖиИвд╝Ж│╝ Ж░ЎВЮ┤ Вќ┤вќц ВЮ┤в▓цьіИЖ░ђ в░юВЃЮьЋўвЕ┤ ЖхгЖ░ёВЮ┤ ВІюВъЉвљўвЕ░ ьЋ┤вІ╣ ЖхгЖ░ёВЌљВёювіћ ВЮ┤в▓цьіИЖ░ђ Вхювїђ 1в▓ѕвДї ВІцьќЅвљювІц.</p>\n<h2 id=\"21-throttle-hook-Жхгьўё\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#21-throttle-hook-%EA%B5%AC%ED%98%84\" aria-label=\"21 throttle hook Жхгьўё permalink\" class=\"anchor-header before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" height=\"20\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"20\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>2.1 Throttle Hook Жхгьўё</h2>\n<div\n              class=\"gatsby-code-button-container\"\n              data-toaster-id=\"1590476217338077200\"\n              data-toaster-class=\"gatsby-code-button-toaster\"\n              data-toaster-text-class=\"gatsby-code-button-toaster-text\"\n              data-toaster-text=\"­ЪЊІ  ВйћвЊювЦ╝ в│хВѓгьќѕВіхвІѕвІц.\"\n              data-toaster-duration=\"3000\"\n              onClick=\"copyToClipboard(`interface throttleProps<T> {\r\n  callback: () => void;\r\n  delay: number;\r\n}\r\n\r\n// ВаюВќ┤ьЋўЖ│аВъљ ьЋўвіћ ьЋИвЊцвЪгвЦ╝ callbackВю╝вАю в░ЏВЋё throttleВЮё Жхгьўё\r\nfunction useThrottle({ callback, delay }: throttleProps<T>): void {\r\n  const lastRun = useRef(Date.now());\r\n\r\n  return () => {\r\n    const timeElapsed = Date.now() - lastRun.current;\r\n    // Ж░ёЖ▓ЕВЮ┤ьЏё в░юВЃЮьЋю ВЮ┤в▓цьіИвДї ВІцьќЅ\r\n    if(timeElapsed >= delay) {\r\n      callback();\r\n      lastRun.current = Date.now();\r\n    }\r\n  }\r\n}`, `1590476217338077200`)\"\n            >\n              <div\n                class=\"gatsby-code-button\"\n                data-tooltip=\"\"\n              >\n                copy<svg stroke=\"currentColor\" fill=\"none\" stroke-width=\"2\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" class=\"h-4 w-4\" height=\"1em\" width=\"1em\" xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\"><path d=\"M16 4h2a2 2 0 0 1 2 2v14a2 2 0 0 1-2 2H6a2 2 0 0 1-2-2V6a2 2 0 0 1 2-2h2\"></path><rect x=\"8\" y=\"2\" width=\"8\" height=\"4\" rx=\"1\" ry=\"1\"></rect></svg>\n              </div>\n            </div>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"ts\"><pre class=\"language-ts\"><code class=\"language-ts\"><span class=\"token keyword\">interface</span> <span class=\"token class-name\">throttleProps<span class=\"token operator\">&lt;</span><span class=\"token constant\">T</span><span class=\"token operator\">></span></span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\r\n  <span class=\"token function-variable function\">callback</span><span class=\"token operator\">:</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span> <span class=\"token operator\">=></span> <span class=\"token keyword\">void</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\r\n  delay<span class=\"token operator\">:</span> <span class=\"token builtin\">number</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\r\n<span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span>\r\n\r\n<span class=\"token comment\">// ВаюВќ┤ьЋўЖ│аВъљ ьЋўвіћ ьЋИвЊцвЪгвЦ╝ callbackВю╝вАю в░ЏВЋё throttleВЮё Жхгьўё</span>\r\n<span class=\"token keyword\">function</span> <span class=\"token function\">useThrottle</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span> callback<span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> delay <span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span><span class=\"token operator\">:</span> throttleProps<span class=\"token operator\">&lt;</span><span class=\"token constant\">T</span><span class=\"token operator\">></span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token operator\">:</span> <span class=\"token keyword\">void</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\r\n  <span class=\"token keyword\">const</span> lastRun <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> <span class=\"token function\">useRef</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span>Date<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token function\">now</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\r\n\r\n  <span class=\"token keyword\">return</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span> <span class=\"token operator\">=></span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\r\n    <span class=\"token keyword\">const</span> timeElapsed <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> Date<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token function\">now</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span> <span class=\"token operator\">-</span> lastRun<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span>current<span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\r\n    <span class=\"token comment\">// Ж░ёЖ▓ЕВЮ┤ьЏё в░юВЃЮьЋю ВЮ┤в▓цьіИвДї ВІцьќЅ</span>\r\n    <span class=\"token keyword\">if</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span>timeElapsed <span class=\"token operator\">>=</span> delay<span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\r\n      <span class=\"token function\">callback</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\r\n      lastRun<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span>current <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> Date<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token function\">now</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\r\n    <span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span>\r\n  <span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span>\r\n<span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span></code></pre></div>\n<h2 id=\"3-debounceВЎђ-throttleВЮў-В░еВЮ┤Ваљ\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#3-debounce%EC%99%80-throttle%EC%9D%98-%EC%B0%A8%EC%9D%B4%EC%A0%90\" aria-label=\"3 debounceВЎђ throttleВЮў В░еВЮ┤Ваљ permalink\" class=\"anchor-header before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" height=\"20\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"20\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>3. DebounceВЎђ ThrottleВЮў В░еВЮ┤Ваљ</h2>\n<ul>\n<li><code class=\"language-text\">Debounce</code>віћ ВЌ░ВєЇВаЂВЮИ ВЮ┤в▓цьіИвЦ╝ ВхюВбЁВаЂВю╝вАю 1в▓ѕвДї ВІцьќЅвљўвЈёвАЮ ьЋювІц.</li>\n<li><code class=\"language-text\">Throttle</code>ВЮђ ВЌ░ВєЇВаЂВЮИ ВЮ┤в▓цьіИвЦ╝ ВЮ╝ВаЋ ВІюЖ░ё вЈЎВЋѕ ВБ╝ЖИ░ВаЂВю╝вАю ВІцьќЅвљўвЈёвАЮ ьЋювІц.</li>\n</ul>\n<h3 id=\"31-ВќИВаю-вг┤ВЌЄВЮё-ВѓгВџЕьЋ┤ВЋ╝-ьЋаЖ╣ї\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#31-%EC%96%B8%EC%A0%9C-%EB%AC%B4%EC%97%87%EC%9D%84-%EC%82%AC%EC%9A%A9%ED%95%B4%EC%95%BC-%ED%95%A0%EA%B9%8C\" aria-label=\"31 ВќИВаю вг┤ВЌЄВЮё ВѓгВџЕьЋ┤ВЋ╝ ьЋаЖ╣ї permalink\" class=\"anchor-header before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" 